<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation à rejoindre un groupe - StudySprint</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1e293b;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D4ED8 0%, #0891B2 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header .group-avatar {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 64px;
        }
        .header .group-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 4px;
        }
        .header .group-meta {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px 30px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .message-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 3px solid #1D4ED8;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .message-box .label {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6B7280;
            margin: 0 0 4px;
        }
        .message-box .text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #EEF2FF;
            color: #4338CA;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* Method 1: Direct link button */
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #1D4ED8;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .link-fallback {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .link-fallback a {
            color: #1D4ED8;
        }

        /* Separator */
        .separator {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }
        .separator .line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: #E5E7EB;
        }
        .separator .text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* Methods 2 & 3 */
        .methods-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .method-card {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .method-card .method-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }
        .code-box {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .code-value {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1D4ED8;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .method-hint {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .qr-wrapper {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0 0 4px;
        }
        .footer .copyright {
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: #D1D5DB;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        {# ─── Header with group info ─── #}
        <div class="header">
            <div class="group-avatar">
                {{ groupName|slice(0, 2)|upper }}
            </div>
            <p class="group-name">{{ groupName }}</p>
            <p class="group-meta">
                {% if invitation.group.subject %}
                    {{ invitation.group.subject }}
                {% endif %}
            </p>
        </div>

        {# ─── Main content ─── #}
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>
                <strong>{{ inviterName }}</strong> vous invite à rejoindre le groupe d'étude
                <strong>« {{ groupName }} »</strong> sur StudySprint.
            </p>

            {# Optional personal message #}
            {% if invitation.message %}
            <div class="message-box">
                <p class="label">Message :</p>
                <p class="text">« {{ invitation.message }} »</p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {# Role badge #}
            <div>
                <span class="role-badge">
                    Rôle : {{ invitation.role == 'moderator' ? 'Modérateur' : (invitation.role == 'admin' ? 'Administrateur' : 'Membre') }}
                </span>
            </div>

            {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
            {# METHOD 1: Direct link (main CTA button)   #}
            {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{ acceptUrl }}" class="btn-primary">
                    ✅ Accepter l'invitation
                </a>
                <p class="link-fallback">
                    Ou copiez ce lien dans votre navigateur :<br>
                    <a href="{{ acceptUrl }}">{{ acceptUrl }}</a>
                </p>
            </div>

            {# Separator #}
            <div class="separator">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <span class="text">AUTRES MÉTHODES</span>
                <div class="line"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="methods-row">
                {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
                {# METHOD 2: Invitation code                  #}
                {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
                <div class="method-card">
                    <p class="method-title">📋 Code d'invitation</p>
                    <div class="code-box">
                        <span class="code-value">{{ invitation.code }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="method-hint">
                        Saisissez ce code dans « Rejoindre un groupe » sur StudySprint
                    </p>
                </div>

                {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
                {# METHOD 3: QR Code                          #}
                {# ══════════════════════════════════════════ #}
                <div class="method-card">
                    <p class="method-title">📱 Scanner le QR Code</p>
                    <div class="qr-wrapper">
                        <img src="cid:qr-code" alt="QR Code d'invitation" width="160" height="160" style="display: block;">
                    </div>
                    <p class="method-hint">
                        Scannez avec votre téléphone pour rejoindre le groupe
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# ─── Footer ─── #}
        <div class="footer">
            {% if invitation.expiresAt %}
            <p>Cette invitation expire le <strong>{{ invitation.expiresAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong>.</p>
            {% endif %}
            <p>Si vous n'avez pas demandé cette invitation, ignorez simplement cet email.</p>
            <p class="copyright">© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} StudySprint — Apprendre ensemble, réussir ensemble.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
